FlightEDA Runbook (see README for full steps)
=============================================

- Instantiate once:
  JULIA_DEPOT_PATH=./.julia_depot ./julia-1.10.5/bin/julia --project=. -e 'using Pkg; Pkg.instantiate()'
- Run all phases (sample config):
  JULIA_DEPOT_PATH=./.julia_depot ./julia-1.10.5/bin/julia --project=. bin/flight_eda.jl --phase all --config config/eda_config_sample.toml
- Single phase (1/2/3/smoke):
  JULIA_DEPOT_PATH=./.julia_depot ./julia-1.10.5/bin/julia --project=. bin/flight_eda.jl --phase 2 --config config/eda_config.toml
- Smoke test shortcut:
  JULIA_DEPOT_PATH=./.julia_depot ./julia-1.10.5/bin/julia --project=. test/smoke_test.jl
- Run tests:
  JULIA_DEPOT_PATH=./.julia_depot ./julia-1.10.5/bin/julia --project=. -e 'using Pkg; Pkg.test()'
- Config override: set EDA_CONFIG to a custom TOML path.
